{"tid":1651742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係電視見到 TKO便衣拉人","createTime":"2019-10-13T12:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T12:33:14.000Z","uid":261897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"14ddc443956246d0a78a26652c32cd853b5f21d9","tid":1651742,"uid":261897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:32:05.000Z","msg":"唔該小心保護自己，望清楚你周邊既人，唔好只係望住你地前面。<br />\n由其係自己一個人行街，得閒郁下條頸！望望左 望望右 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">望望後</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.特別係4，5個人一齊，身型一致健碩<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">帶得口罩，面罩又唔係個個著全黑衫</span></span><br />\n3.佢地會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大叫反警口號</span></span>，引你不主覺走近左佢地。<br />\n4.佢地會係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有防暴係附近既時候</span></span>做野，因佢會快速叫人支援<br />\n<br />\n我<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真係真係真係</span></strong>係電視見到，唔係要做ghostbusters，只求大家<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">睇路</span></span>。"},{"pid":"73eb2570e0e2bf653786457feb44bce8a59bdfed","tid":1651742,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:32:45.000Z","msg":"【18禁】班狗平時係威係勢 原來不過係賤犬一條<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651603</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"00340d11fc8c100820bd11333bbce8de23904c97","tid":1651742,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"【以正視聽】已FC！今日割頸嘅係中共特務嫁禍示威者所為，早前連登巴打已預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651683</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}